Package model.player.damagetrack

Class NumColour

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.player.damagetrack.NumColour
  • public class NumColour
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles the occurrences of a given colour in the killtrack and damage track while monitoring ties between colours.
